\hspace*{2cm}$\bullet$ $\varphi_{xx}(0)\geq|\varphi_{xx}(\tau)|\quad$\cite{COU:97}\\
\hspace*{2cm}$\bullet$ $\varphi_{xx}(\tau)\geq (X_0)^2-\sigma^2\quad$\cite{GIR:RAB:STE:05}
