\varphi_{xy}(\tau) = \lim_{T\rightarrow\infty} \frac {1} {T} \int\limits_{-T/2}^{T/2}x(t)y(t-\tau)dt = \lim_{T\rightarrow\infty}\frac {1} {T} \int\limits_{-T/2}^{T/2} x(t+\tau)y(t)dt.
